translate Schinese chapter4_fb35396d:

    # "He heard James breathing."
    "James的呼吸声传入了他的耳朵。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:13
translate Schinese chapter4_81008708:

    # "As Edgar blinked his eyes, he saw James' chest coming up and down right in front of him."
    "Edgar眨眨眼，看到James的双峰在他面前有节奏地起伏。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:15
translate Schinese chapter4_90e87dca:

    # "The fox was grasping onto James' arm, and his legs were wrapped around him too."
    "狐狸正抱着James的胳膊，双腿还紧紧缠着对方。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:17
translate Schinese chapter4_636b6969:

    # "Edgar gulped."
    "Edgar咽了口唾沫。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:19
translate Schinese chapter4_dc32eb8c:

    # e "Oh... oh no."
    e "哦...不，不。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:21
translate Schinese chapter4_00f810d4:

    # e "I hope he didn't notice..."
    e "希望他没有注意吧..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:24
translate Schinese chapter4_40289db6:

    # "He slowly removed himself, but even as he did so he noticed his hand grazing James' fur."
    "他慢慢挪开身子，与此同时，他的手无意间擦过James的毛。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:26
translate Schinese chapter4_ee3ffd98:

    # "His bicep was so big, yet soft to the touch."
    "对方的二头肌大得惊人，触感却十分柔软。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:28
translate Schinese chapter4_d7a18cba:

    # "Edgar gulped again, feeling his dick stiffen a bit."
    "Edgar又咽了口唾沫，感到自己的小兄弟微微抬起了头。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:30
translate Schinese chapter4_f4d0485c:

    # "Even James' overall big size caught Edgar's attention. He recalled when James had accidentally slept on him."
    "就连James的大块头也抓住了Edgar的眼球。他回想起有一次，James不小心睡在他身上的情景。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:32
translate Schinese chapter4_f1ef9d7f:

    # "He liked feeling small under Jame's heavy muscular body."
    "他喜欢小小的自己被压在James肌肉发达的身体下。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:34
translate Schinese chapter4_89975f0e:

    # e "Ugh, not now! Imagine if he woke up-"
    e "咳咳，现在不行！要是他醒了-"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:36
translate Schinese chapter4_9d22c12e:

    # "He slowly removed himself, feeling himself blush as his hand grazed James' fur."
    "他慢慢挪开了身子，感到自己满脸通红。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:41
translate Schinese chapter4_d90463cd:

    # "Edgar lifted himself up off the bed and skulked quietly to the bathroom."
    "Edgar爬下床，悄悄溜进了浴室。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:43
translate Schinese chapter4_3ac786e8:

    # "He turned on the shower, and after the water was warm, he stepped in."
    "他打开淋浴器，待水热后走了进去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:45
translate Schinese chapter4_fa22368c:

    # e "That was a close one. I hope he didn't notice me clinging on like that."
    e "好险啊。希望他没有注意到我抱着他不放。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:47
translate Schinese chapter4_e2b46059:

    # "Edgar rinsed himself, and felt a little remorse. James was so beautiful, and so caring. But..."
    "Edgar带着些许自责冲了个澡。James那么帅，又那么体贴，可是..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:49
translate Schinese chapter4_303b9bfa:

    # "He decided to push the though out for now."
    "他决定暂时把这个问题抛开。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:51
translate Schinese chapter4_62950eef:

    # "After he finished showering, he noticed a text from Max."
    "洗完之后，他看到Max发来一条短信。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:53
translate Schinese chapter4_20a113b5:

    # m "Hey, so what happened??"
    m "嘿，怎么样了？？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:55
translate Schinese chapter4_45a4a53b:

    # "Edgar thought about it, and decided to keep it simple for now."
    "Edgar思考了下，决定先不想那么复杂。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:57
translate Schinese chapter4_c474dc13:

    # e "Met up with Mary, but she didn't want the chip back. Long story, I'll tell you about it later."
    e "和Mary见了一面，但她不想拿回芯片。说来话长，我之后再告诉你。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:59
translate Schinese chapter4_2db89d2a:

    # m "Ok, interesting. Keep me posted!"
    m "有意思，好的，保持联系！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:61
translate Schinese chapter4_032ac1af:

    # "Edgar guessed he would meet up with everyone later and recount everything. At this point, there was no rush."
    "Edgar想将大伙约出来，并把事情的经过一五一十讲给他们听，不过现在还不急。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:67
translate Schinese chapter4_d1633d3d:

    # "Edgar arrived at the taco shop as usual. His head was feeling cloudy."
    "Edgar像往常一样来到塔可店，他感到自己的脑袋晕沉沉的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:73
translate Schinese chapter4_f5860fed:

    # jess "Hey, Sug'. How's it going?"
    jess "你好啊，亲。最近怎么样？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:75
translate Schinese chapter4_8a8077e6:

    # e "Pretty good, had a long night... how about you?"
    e "挺好的，度过了漫长的一夜...你呢？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:77
translate Schinese chapter4_3806ef73:

    # jess "Just fine, thanks for asking!"
    jess "都好，谢谢关心！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:79
translate Schinese chapter4_9c0d5e74:

    # "Edgar walked into the kitchen."
    "Edgar走进厨房。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:87
translate Schinese chapter4_f64228c2:

    # a "Hey, happy hump day!"
    a "嗨，驼峰日快乐！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:89
translate Schinese chapter4_45e1f815:

    # e "Thanks, boss. You too."
    e "谢谢，老板。你也是。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:91
translate Schinese chapter4_4f679478:

    # a "Everything alright? You look at little rough."
    a "一切都好吗？你看起来不太精神的样子。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:95
translate Schinese chapter4_4eb17fe3:

    # e "Yeah, not bad really. Just tired."
    e "还好啦，就是有点累。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:97
translate Schinese chapter4_6bfaf3fe:

    # a "Ah I see. I stayed up pretty late myself. I found a cool new horror game that I played the heck out of."
    a "啊，我懂，我自己也熬到很晚才睡。我找到个新出的恐怖游戏，一口气玩儿了个爽。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:101
translate Schinese chapter4_cd2a48fe:

    # e "Oh yeah? What was it about?"
    e "是吗？什么剧情？"

