translate Schinese chapter4_d827162f:

    # a "Well it's a bit dark in theme. It's about PTSD."
    a "关于PTSD的，主题有点儿阴暗。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:105
translate Schinese chapter4_3975d757:

    # "Ari threw a bunch of meat on the grill and it started sizzling loudly."
    "Ari往烤架上扔了一堆肉，空气中顿时响起了咝咝声。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:107
translate Schinese chapter4_f2fda39a:

    # e "That sounds heavy."
    e "听起来有些沉重。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:109
translate Schinese chapter4_88e5c578:

    # a "Yeah it was really interesting though. It's about a guy dealing with loneliness after coming back from a war."
    a "确实，不过还真蛮有趣的。讲了一个从战场上归来的男人如何应对孤独的故事。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:111
translate Schinese chapter4_0737180e:

    # a "He kind of just drifts through life unable to cope with his mental issues."
    a "他无法处理自己的精神问题，过着漫无目的的生活。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:113
translate Schinese chapter4_deec2c36:

    # e "What happens with him?"
    e "他怎么了？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:115
translate Schinese chapter4_99bd1743:

    # a "So you play through his memories and experiences. Some are happy memories and others are sad."
    a "游戏流程就是他的记忆和经历。有快乐的，也有悲伤的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:117
translate Schinese chapter4_18114eba:

    # a "At the end depending on your choices, he reacts in different ways."
    a "在最后，根据你的选择，他会做出不同的反应。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:119
translate Schinese chapter4_169c3127:

    # a "But there is no truly 'happy' ending. It's just him learning to live with it."
    a "但是没有真正意义上的‘快乐’结局，他只是在学会接受现实。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:121
translate Schinese chapter4_328ac451:

    # e "That sounds kinda depressing."
    e "听起来有点抑郁。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:123
translate Schinese chapter4_2a3040dc:

    # "Ari shrugged."
    "Ari耸耸肩。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:125
translate Schinese chapter4_73469417:

    # a "Sometimes it's good to have a little hit of reality every now and then... not always though."
    a "偶尔接触下现实也不错...只不过别太过。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:127
translate Schinese chapter4_6361c8c3:

    # e "Yeah..."
    e "是啊..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:133
translate Schinese chapter4_5c404f8b:

    # "They continued their day, chatting about random things."
    "他们杂七杂八闲聊起来，继续着自己的工作。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:135
translate Schinese chapter4_38acd7b6:

    # "Finally, might-time came. the dinner rush ended, and they started closing up."
    "终于，晚餐高峰结束了，他们准备打样。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:145
translate Schinese chapter4_cba1a7c7:

    # a "So you never told me... did that 'thing' go OK?"
    a "所以你还没告诉我...那件‘事’怎么样了？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:147
translate Schinese chapter4_95a2a85a:

    # e "Oh... yeah. It went alright I guess. I mean I'm still in one piece, huh?"
    e "哦...应该还算顺利吧。我的意思是，我还活着？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:149
translate Schinese chapter4_a8344a07:

    # "Ari used his muscles to scrape the grill and clean it."
    "Ari用他的肌肉把烤架刮得干干净净。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:151
translate Schinese chapter4_e77fa8b3:

    # a "Were you in some kind of trouble?"
    a "遇到什么麻烦了吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:158
translate Schinese chapter4_22fded4e:

    # e "Yeah, I guess you could say that."
    e "嗯，可以这么说。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:160
translate Schinese chapter4_9853e250:

    # e "I... stole something. And some people are after it."
    e "我...偷了一件东西。有人追了过来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:162
translate Schinese chapter4_25af5dc9:

    # a "What did you steal?"
    a "你偷了什么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:164
translate Schinese chapter4_bc39d732:

    # e "It's like a computer chip of sorts."
    e "有点像电脑芯片。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:166
translate Schinese chapter4_b70b3741:

    # a "Hmm. What does it do? And why did you take it?"
    a "唔，它有什么作用？你为什么要把它偷走？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:168
translate Schinese chapter4_73d4218c:

    # e "It's a long story... but basically I don't know what it does, I thought it was a jewelry box or something."
    e "说来话长...不过我压根不知道它是用来干嘛的，我还以为只是珠宝盒什么的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:170
translate Schinese chapter4_428f1402:

    # e "I tried to give it back to the original owner... but she didn't want it."
    e "我试着把它还给原来的主人...但她不肯收。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:172
translate Schinese chapter4_50b8483b:

    # a "Why not?"
    a "为什么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:174
translate Schinese chapter4_33c93a8d:

    # e "I still don't know. She said it's dangerous. And some bad people are watching her."
    e "我到现在也不知道。她说那东西很危险，还说有坏人在监视她。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:176
translate Schinese chapter4_660a0c15:

    # "Ari continued cleaning the grill."
    "Ari还在清理烤架。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:178
translate Schinese chapter4_36f79692:

    # e "I also think the same people might be after me. Whatever it is, it must be important."
    e "我觉得可能跟追踪我的是同一批人。无论如何，那东西一定非常重要。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:180
translate Schinese chapter4_56f8f679:

    # "Ari crossed his arms."
    "Ari抱起双臂。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:182
translate Schinese chapter4_68c65225:

    # a "Keep your wits about you, kid."
    a "保持警惕吧，小子。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:184
translate Schinese chapter4_f5b478b0:

    # a "You've been a good friend ever since I met you. I've known petty thieves, but you have a moral code. I can sense it."
    a "自遇见你以来，我就觉得你是位好朋友。我认识不少小偷，但你是一个有道德准则的人，我能感觉到。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:186
translate Schinese chapter4_bf0f4748:

    # e "I guess you could say that. And thanks, you've been a good friend too."
    e "我想可以这么说。谢谢，你也是我的好朋友。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:188
translate Schinese chapter4_4ae16ac4:

    # a "If you need me to walk you home, I can do that."
    a "如果你需要我陪你回家的话，只管开口。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:192
translate Schinese chapter4_7035a9b4:

    # e "Yeah that would be great, thank you."
    e "那就太好了，谢谢你。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:196
translate Schinese chapter4_438b0deb:

    # a "No sweat!"
    a "没什么！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:200
translate Schinese chapter4_0f1298e6:

    # "After they finished cleaning, Ari took Edgar back to the apartment."
    "他们打扫完毕，Ari送Edgar回到了公寓。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:202
translate Schinese chapter4_fbedd89e:

    # "The streets were mostly empty, and Edgar didn't get a sense like he was being followed."
    "街道上空无一人，Edgar也没有被跟踪的感觉。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:204
translate Schinese chapter4_d31caed5:

    # "He appreciated the company anyway."
    "不过他还是很感激对方的陪伴。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:206
translate Schinese chapter4_399a9d01:

    # "When Ari dropped Edgar off, he surprised him with a hug."
    "在Edgar下车时，Ari给了他一个意外的拥抱。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:208
translate Schinese chapter4_e8da7640:

    # a "Take care of yourself."
    a "照顾好自己。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:210
translate Schinese chapter4_22ff56cb:

    # e "A-alright, you too..."
    e "好-好的，你也是..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:212
translate Schinese chapter4_73b350be:

    # a "See ya next time!"
    a "下次见咯！"

