translate Schinese chapter4_5cb9476b:

    # a "OK, well stay safe out there."
    a "好吧，在外面注意安全。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:225
translate Schinese chapter4_f199688f:

    # "They finished cleaning up, and Edgar walked back home alone."
    "他们打扫完毕，Edgar独自回到了家中。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:227
translate Schinese chapter4_afe4fca8:

    # "He kept his ears perked up, but didn't hear anything suspicious."
    "他一路竖起耳朵，却并没有听到任何可疑的动静。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:233
translate Schinese chapter4_c682d99e:

    # e "I was in trouble, but don't worry about it. I'll be fine."
    e "我是有麻烦了，不过别担心，我没问题的。"

