    # e "Will do."
    e "我会的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:258
translate Schinese chapter4_a5bfe3a4_1:

    # "They finished cleaning up, and Edgar walked back home."
    "他们打扫完毕，Edgar走回了家。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:266
translate Schinese chapter4_97594201:

    # "Edgar walked into the apartment, tired from standing all day."
    "Edgar拖着站了一整天的疲惫身体走进公寓。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:268
translate Schinese chapter4_faeea8c8:

    # j "Hey, Edgar!"
    j "嗨，Edgar！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:270
translate Schinese chapter4_69319bf1:

    # e "Hey!"
    e "嗨！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:272
translate Schinese chapter4_141ec683:

    # j "Come in here! I just started watching this depressed horse show. You'll love it."
    j "快进来！我刚开始看一个抑郁的马的节目，你一定喜欢。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:274
translate Schinese chapter4_aad5e7fa:

    # e "(Gosh, who knew there would be so much depression-related media?)"
    e "（天，怎么有这么多跟抑郁相关的媒体？）"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:276
translate Schinese chapter4_bc137d5e:

    # e "Alright, coming!"
    e "知道了，这就来！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:282
translate Schinese chapter4_54dfcd94:

    # "Edgar went into the bedroom and jumped in next to James."
    "Edgar走进卧室，跳到James旁边。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:284
translate Schinese chapter4_bf237dd3:

    # "The show was more funny than Edgar expected, although that horse was definitely depressed."
    "这个节目比Edgar预想的要有趣得多，尽管那匹马确实很抑郁。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:286
translate Schinese chapter4_4e70f0eb:

    # "Edgar could feel himself relating to some of what the horse was going through."
    "Edgar感到自己与那匹马的经历产生了共鸣。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:288
translate Schinese chapter4_9bcb7ffd:

    # "Sometimes he did feel like life was full of despair."
    "有时，他感觉生活充满了绝望。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:290
translate Schinese chapter4_3b3e4bd3:

    # "But other times, he chrished those small moments where he wished time stood still."
    "但偶尔也有值得珍重的，他希望永远不会结束的小小瞬间。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:292
translate Schinese chapter4_6c98eeaf:

    # "Even now, watching this show with James, he could feel a warm and cozy aura around him."
    "即便是现在，和James一起看这个节目的时候，他也能感到自己被温暖和舒适所包围。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:294
translate Schinese chapter4_6385e380:

    # j "So I was thinking.. wanna go to the trail again tomorrow?"
    j "话说我在想...明天要不要再去山里一趟？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:296
translate Schinese chapter4_521849e0:

    # e "But I wanted to be lazy!"
    e "我想偷个懒诶！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:298
translate Schinese chapter4_bb18cb91:

    # j "Alright, how about this. If you go with me all the way to the top, I'll get you donuts on the way down."
    j "好吧，那这样呢：如果你陪我爬山，我就在回来的路上奖励你甜甜圈。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:300
translate Schinese chapter4_fdaaee2c:

    # e "How dare you use my greatest weakness... baked... goods!!"
    e "竟敢利用我最大的弱点...烘焙食物！！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:302
translate Schinese chapter4_6b835ccb:

    # j "I'm a sadistic bastard sometimes, eh?"
    j "我偶尔会变身抖s哦？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:304
translate Schinese chapter4_e9a3cdca:

    # "James smirked."
    "James得意地笑了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:306
translate Schinese chapter4_d480fae8:

    # e "Fine. But we should be careful and not attract any attention."
    e "好吧。可咱们应该小心，不引起任何注意才对。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:308
translate Schinese chapter4_268015f2:

    # j "I know. It's just... there's something really pretty up there. I didn't get to show it to you last time."
    j "我知道。不过...山顶上有很棒的东西，我上次还没让你看过。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:310
translate Schinese chapter4_f6fc1908:

    # e "Oh yeah? What is it?"
    e "噢？是什么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:312
translate Schinese chapter4_501085be:

    # j "It's a surprise. I wouldn't dare ruin it."
    j "我可不想破坏惊喜。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:314
translate Schinese chapter4_1d1c4339:

    # e "Alright, it better be amazing though."
    e "好吧，最好足够惊喜。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:316
translate Schinese chapter4_0e351071:

    # j "It is. You'll love it."
    j "足足的，你一定喜欢。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:318
translate Schinese chapter4_4b4249f8:

    # "They watched the show for a while longer, and then it was lights out."
    "他们又看了会节目，然后熄了灯。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:322
translate Schinese chapter4_02069001:

    # "Again, Edgar listened to the sound of James breathing in and out."
    "James的呼吸声再次传入了Edgar的耳朵。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:324
translate Schinese chapter4_e82945ff:

    # "He felt peace, like he was sleeping on the soft night clouds."
    "他感到平静，就像睡在软绵绵的云朵上。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:326
translate Schinese chapter4_34ef6789:

    # "He sank into the clouds until he slept."
    "他沉入云端，直至睡去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:332
translate Schinese chapter4_d06e909f:

    # "Edgar woke up and did his usual routine, with James waking up a bit later."
    "Edgar比James稍早醒来，并做了日常的洗漱。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:334
translate Schinese chapter4_9f2018bd:

    # "As he sipped his coffee, he thought about everything that happened up to that point."
    "他一边喝着咖啡，一边回忆着之前的点点滴滴。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:338
translate Schinese chapter4_8c73d82f:

    # "He wasn't sure how to move forward, except taking it day by day."
    "他不知该如何继续前行，只能走一步，算一步。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:340
translate Schinese chapter4_d68cffc0:

    # "Today was just a day to relax and nothing more."
    "今天只是个放松的日子，没别的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:342
translate Schinese chapter4_28888921:

    # "After a while, James joined him. His fur was still wet from the morning shower."
    "没过多久，James也来了，带着一身洗完澡后湿漉漉的毛。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:348
translate Schinese chapter4_13d84412:

    # j "Hey! Whatcha thinkin about?"
    j "嘿！想什么呐？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:350
translate Schinese chapter4_214baa5a:

    # e "You know, the usual stuff."
    e "一些琐事，你知道的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:352
translate Schinese chapter4_f5de479c:

    # j "You're thinking about the donuts we're gonna get aren't you?"
    j "比如要哪种甜甜圈吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:356
translate Schinese chapter4_e27236c2:

    # e "Haha, yep! Totally caught me."
    e "哈哈，是啊！被你发现了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:358
translate Schinese chapter4_d28bec1c:

    # "James smirked and rubbed Edgar's back."
    "James咧嘴一笑，抚摸着Edgar的后背。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:360
translate Schinese chapter4_8a6abf8f:

    # j "I can't blame you. You're gonna love 'em."
    j "倒也不怪你，你一定会爱上它们的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:362
translate Schinese chapter4_0ae3bf6a:

    # "Edgar felt a bit of blood rush to his face as he felt the wolf's large paws on him."
    "Edgar感受着自己身上那只大狼爪，气血一点点涌上头。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:364
translate Schinese chapter4_7a1c65bc:

    # e "So when are we leaving?"
    e "所以咱们什么时候出发？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:366
translate Schinese chapter4_f6a4b3d1:

    # j "Ooh, what an eager beaver! Well I'm all ready to go!"
    j "喔~，真是个积极的小伙子！我已经准备好了！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:370
translate Schinese chapter4_dff47e7f:

    # e "Alright, let's get it over with!"
    e "好，咱们速战速决！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:372
translate Schinese chapter4_e0a6f31d:

    # j "That's the spirit!"
    j "这才对嘛！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:382
translate Schinese chapter4_bf6e5089:

    # j "Alright! We're here!"
    j "耶！咱们到喽！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:384
translate Schinese chapter4_b98765fc:

    # e "*Pant* Hey, wait up! You walk too fast!"
    e "*喘气声* 嘿，慢一点儿！你走太快了！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:386
translate Schinese chapter4_43390b56:

    # j "Oh, sorry."
    j "噢，不好意思啦。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:388
translate Schinese chapter4_a43dab7e:

    # "James scratched his head, looking cheerfully amused."
    "James挠着头，一副兴高采烈的模样。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:390
translate Schinese chapter4_af68371d:

    # "They continued the path, going higher into the hills."
    "他们沿着同一条路，往更高的山而去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:398
translate Schinese chapter4_89f21622:

    # j "So I've been thinking about some things."
    j "话说，我一直在想一件事。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:400
translate Schinese chapter4_efe5222c:

    # e "Yeah?"
    e "嗯？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:402
translate Schinese chapter4_dad3d36d:

    # j "Time seems to be going by so quickly nowadays. Not like when I was a kid - a year felt like it was an eternity."
    j "现在的时间真是飞一样快啊。不像小时候-过一年就像过了一辈子。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:404
translate Schinese chapter4_10743698:

    # e "Yeah I get the same impression."
    e "是啊，我有同感。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:406
translate Schinese chapter4_c0e02bc4:

    # j "Do you ever wonder where you'll be in the future?"
    j "你有想过自己的将来吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:408
translate Schinese chapter4_c92c3de1:

    # e "The... future? I'm not sure. I haven't really thought about it."
    e "...将来？不知道。我没有想过。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:410
translate Schinese chapter4_dc751bd0:

    # j "For me... There's gotta be more than just working and paying bills, you know?"
    j "对我来说...将来不仅仅是工作和还账单，你明白吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:412
translate Schinese chapter4_3b1acb6d:

    # e "Yeah, that's true.. but at least you get paid well right? And excitement isn't always good... I mean look at me."
    e "是啊，确实...但起码你的收入还不错，不是吗？刺激并不总是件好事...我是说，看看我。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:414
translate Schinese chapter4_f840b7fc:

    # j "Haha, I guess you're right..."
    j "哈哈，说的也是..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:416
translate Schinese chapter4_09e4762a:

    # "Edgar thought about his own life."
    "Edgar思考过自己的人生。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:419
translate Schinese chapter4_434238c3:

    # "He still wanted to get rich and live the rockstar life. But for what purpose? Wouldn't things get.. boring?"
    "他还是想发财，过上摇滚巨星的生活。但这又有什么意义呢？这样的人生不会变得...无聊吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:421
translate Schinese chapter4_88e3b921:

    # "What came after that?"
    "再然后呢？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:423
translate Schinese chapter4_bbade3a4:

    # "He still had this idea of being some sort of anti-hero... just like Raven Cap."
    "他仍怀着成为反英雄的念头...就像Raven Cap那样。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:425
translate Schinese chapter4_e95a8fd3:

    # "But those were just his comic book fantasies weren't they?"
    "但这不过是漫画书中的幻想，不是吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:427
translate Schinese chapter4_af4314d5:

    # "Reality wasn't so romantic."
    "现实并没有那么浪漫。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:429
translate Schinese chapter4_ed97ac27:

    # "He wanted to live... but for what purpose?"
    "他想要活着...可是为了什么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:431
translate Schinese chapter4_63e5e772:

    # "There had to be a reason to get up and keep going. Something to keep fighting for."
    "一定有一个我们可以爬起来继续前进的理由，一个我们可以为之奋斗的目标。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:433
translate Schinese chapter4_f698c6e6:

    # "In his heart, he felt something. The spark of a wish, to be closer to someone. To be held and loved."
    "他在内心深处感觉到了什么。希望的火花。他渴望接近一个人，被拥抱，被爱。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:435
translate Schinese chapter4_bd0a8217:

    # "It's the only thing he wanted, but he couldn't admit it. How embarassing would it be?"
    "这就是他唯一想要的。可是他说不出口，没人知道会有多尴尬。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:437
translate Schinese chapter4_1a96d938:

    # "He still didn't know what he wanted. No matter how much he tried, he couldn't picture his future in his head."
    "他依然不知道自己想要什么。无论他怎样努力，也描绘不出自己的未来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:439
translate Schinese chapter4_5afdcd0d:

    # e "I dunno. I guess I don't think about that stuff too often. I can't even picture what tomorrow's like, much less the future."
    e "不知道，我不经常思考那些东西。我连明天是什么样子都想象不到，更别提将来了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:441
translate Schinese chapter4_b072c492:

    # j "Well, that's OK. I probably think about stuff like that too much."
    j "唔，好吧，也许是我想太多了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:443
translate Schinese chapter4_1e7869b8:

    # j "Sometimes I forget to enjoy the moment."
    j "有时候，我会忘记享受当下。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:447
translate Schinese chapter4_8304a45c:

    # "They came up to the walls of rock."
    "他们爬上了岩壁。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:449
translate Schinese chapter4_a5d0e2f4:

    # j "After you!"
    j "你先请！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:451
translate Schinese chapter4_59e1860e:

    # e "Thanks! And you better not rush me."
    e "谢了！还有你最好别催我。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:453
translate Schinese chapter4_8df124e1:

    # j "Hurry up!"
    j "赶紧的！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:455
translate Schinese chapter4_e9a3cdca_1:

    # "James smirked."
    "James坏笑着说道。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:457
translate Schinese chapter4_394e4179:

    # "They passed through the narrow passage, and kept walking."
    "他们穿过狭窄的通道，继续向前。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:461
translate Schinese chapter4_1683d2f5:

    # j "Look, that's where we sat last time. But let's go further."
    j "看，那是咱们之前坐的地方，这次再走远一点。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:463
translate Schinese chapter4_d3051b9a:

    # e "Alright... I hope we're there soon. I'm getting tired."
    e "好吧...希望不会太远，我有点累了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:465
translate Schinese chapter4_76f93cbe:

    # j "Don't worry we'll be there before you know it."
    j "别担心，一眨眼的功夫就到。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:467
translate Schinese chapter4_249cb644:

    # "The path kept going up, and the woods started to become denser."
    "沿着小路上行，树林变得茂密起来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:469
translate Schinese chapter4_659e562d:

    # "There was a booming roll of thunder."
    "远方雷鸣滚滚。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:471
translate Schinese chapter4_610393ad:

    # e "Was it supposed to rain today?"
    e "今天有雨吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:473
translate Schinese chapter4_8bbd0735:

    # j "Ah, I dunno. I guess it's going to."
    j "啊，不晓得，应该有吧。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:475
translate Schinese chapter4_284e2540:

    # e "Dangit, I didn't bring an umbrella."
    e "倒霉，我没有带伞。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:477
translate Schinese chapter4_4ef56328:

    # j "It's alright, a little rain won't kill us."
    j "不要紧，一点小雨，杀不死人。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:479
translate Schinese chapter4_8ab9126f:

    # e "I forgot to mention this but... I'm a witch and water will melt me."
    e "忘了告诉你了...我是个女巫，遇水即融。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:481
translate Schinese chapter4_51f32d90:

    # j "Oh no! I guess I'll have to cover you up with my clothes."
    j "哦，不！看来我得用衣服把你遮起来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:483
translate Schinese chapter4_684adb58:

    # e "Eww no thanks I'd rather melt."
    e "噫。不了，谢谢，我宁愿选择融化。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:485
translate Schinese chapter4_f3819d8d:

    # "James laughed."
    "James大笑起来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:487
translate Schinese chapter4_966fd58d:

    # "They kept walking up the hill for quite a long time."
    "他们向上走了很长一段时间。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:489
translate Schinese chapter4_8f8571e7:

    # "Mostly they were quiet, with James pointing out small animals in the trees."
    "James把树林中的小动物指给Edgar看，二人基本上都很安静。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:491
translate Schinese chapter4_ab463a9f:

    # "At some point, James veered off the path sharply."
    "不知过了多久，James突然偏离了小路。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:493
translate Schinese chapter4_f70de743:

    # e "Oh, we're not going on the path anymore."
    e "诶，不走这条路了吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:495
translate Schinese chapter4_cb33241f:

    # j "Yeah, the path is cool but... that's not where we're headed."
    j "嗯，这条路是蛮酷的，不过...不是咱们要去的地方。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:497
translate Schinese chapter4_496ec35a:

    # "The thunder started again as they walked through the dense wood. Small droplets of water began to fall."
    "当他们在茂密的树林中穿行时，雷声再次响了起来，雨点开始滴落。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:499
translate Schinese chapter4_15f91327:

    # e "I guess we're getting wet huh?"
    e "看来要湿身了，哈哈？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:501
translate Schinese chapter4_c881c61d:

    # j "Yep, guess so! We're almost there."
    j "嗯哼！咱们马上就到。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:503
translate Schinese chapter4_bcd935b3:

    # "They continued for a few minutes longer until they reached an almost impenetrable wall of vines."
    "他们又走了几分钟，来到一堵密不透风的藤蔓墙前。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:505
translate Schinese chapter4_24c9cc73:

    # e "What is this?"
    e "这是什么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:507
translate Schinese chapter4_ce5aead5:

    # j "I'm not sure where it comes from, but it's been here forever."
    j "我也不清楚，不过印象里一直都有。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:509
translate Schinese chapter4_99ae2868:

    # "James walked along the wall, looking carefully for something."
    "James沿墙仔细寻找着什么。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:511
translate Schinese chapter4_4912c0dd:

    # j "Here."
    j "找到了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:515
translate Schinese chapter4_265e7db6:

    # "He stuck his foot in a clearing in the vines, and ducked into the vines."
    "他把脚伸到藤蔓的一处空隙中，一头扎了进去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:517
translate Schinese chapter4_df914a79:

    # j "Follow me!"
    j "快跟上！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:519
translate Schinese chapter4_3d8c8fb2:

    # e "Um.. alright I'll give it a shot."
    e "呃...好吧，我尽量。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:521
translate Schinese chapter4_d2a8da77:

    # "Edgar followed James through the vines, going deeper into them."
    "Edgar跟随James穿过藤蔓，往深处走去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:523
translate Schinese chapter4_2012969f:

    # "He found it easy to flex his body through."
    "他发现屈身的话还算轻松。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:525
translate Schinese chapter4_82401a80:

    # "As he was nearing the outer edge of the wall, he tripped -"
    "临近墙的边缘时，他绊了一跤-"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:527
translate Schinese chapter4_aa743ba1:

    # "- but James caught him."
    "-不过James接住了他。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:529
translate Schinese chapter4_28e96d14:

    # "He looked up and saw James' snout grinning in front of him."
    "他抬头望去，映入眼帘的是James灿烂的笑容。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:531
translate Schinese chapter4_d0cd7609:

    # j "Are you OK?"
    j "没事吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:533
translate Schinese chapter4_291f0972:

    # "Edgar noticed he had somehow nestled himself into a warm embrace."
    "Edgar发现不知何时，自己依偎在了一个温暖的怀抱中。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:535
translate Schinese chapter4_58db2a19:

    # e "Y-yeah, sorry..."
    e "没-没事，抱歉..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:537
translate Schinese chapter4_4b4e0698:

    # j "No problem! You're pretty clumsy for a master thief you know."
    j "别客气！知道吗，作为一名大盗，你可真够笨手笨脚的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:539
translate Schinese chapter4_d1f960b3:

    # e "I guess that's why I'm not very good at it!"
    e "所以我才不擅长偷东西吧！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:541
translate Schinese chapter4_cb34491f:

    # "They went a little further and exited through the other side."
    "他们又往前走了几步，从另一边离开了藤蔓墙。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:543
translate Schinese chapter4_fbf0dff5:

    # "Edgar stared in awe at the sight."
    "Edgar敬畏地注视着眼前的景象。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:549
translate Schinese chapter4_40941110:

    # "It was a large metal tower. From the looks of it, it was abandoned."
    "那是一座高大的金属塔，看样子已经被废弃了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:551
translate Schinese chapter4_344f5ba4:

    # j "Cool, huh?"
    j "酷吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:553
translate Schinese chapter4_d23ffe5f:

    # e "Y-Yeah. What is this place?"
    e "是-是诶。这里是什么地方？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:555
translate Schinese chapter4_54998cc9:

    # j "I don't know. But I found it once when I was wandering around here."
    j "不知道，我在附近闲逛时发现的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:557
translate Schinese chapter4_76ab0c4a:

    # j "I haven't seen any trace of anyone else here. It's like a secret area."
    j "目前为止还没在这看到其他人，跟秘密区域似的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:559
translate Schinese chapter4_a3687bf5:

    # e "I can imagine why. Not many people would come wandering through here."
    e "倒也可以理解，毕竟没什么人会来这种地方闲逛。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:561
translate Schinese chapter4_70e111a2:

    # j "Come on, I wanna show you something."
    j "快来，我有东西让你看。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:563
translate Schinese chapter4_a6f653a5:

    # "James led him toward the tower. He went to a set of stairs near the bottom."
    "James领着Edgar来到塔底的楼梯前。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:565
translate Schinese chapter4_3526f7fa:

    # e "Is it safe to climb up?"
    e "结实吗，这楼梯？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:567
translate Schinese chapter4_7b9c1266:

    # j "Yeah! I've done it lots of times. Just be careful, it's a little wet."
    j "放心！我上去过不少次了。不过小心点，有点儿滑。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:569
translate Schinese chapter4_264c12fe:

    # "James started climbing and Edgar followed."
    "James说罢爬了上去，Edgar紧随其后。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:573
translate Schinese chapter4_9aa0e0d2:

    # "As they went up, Edgar could feel the wind grow more intense, and it started to drizzle more."
    "Edgar越是往上，越感觉风刮得厉害，蒙蒙细雨也越下越大了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:577
translate Schinese chapter4_cbe76105:

    # "Finally, they made it onto a platform almost at the very top."
    "最后，他们登上了一个相当接近塔顶的平台。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:579
translate Schinese chapter4_e2736c13:

    # e "W-wow..."
    e "哇-哇喔..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:581
translate Schinese chapter4_f0fa8290:

    # "Edgar could see the entire cityscape beneath them."
    "整个城市的景色尽收Edgar的眼底。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:583
translate Schinese chapter4_11337ec4:

    # e "We're so high up... this is amazing."
    e "好高啊...太神奇了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:585
translate Schinese chapter4_0c6d7847:

    # j "Yeah, it's like a sea of stars isn't it?"
    j "就像一片星星的海洋，是吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:587
translate Schinese chapter4_c2e818fa:

    # e "I feel like I'm floating."
    e "感觉好像漂在天上。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:589
translate Schinese chapter4_befeafaf:

    # "The rain started pouring harder. They were almost soaking wet."
    "雨下得更大了，几乎将他们淋透。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:591
translate Schinese chapter4_9112a302:

    # "James leaned against the railing, and Edgar did too."
    "James靠在了栏杆上，Edgar也一样。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:593
translate Schinese chapter4_010cf1f9:

    # j "I..."
    j "我..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:595
translate Schinese chapter4_1b27dbc6:

    # "James stammered."
    "James结结巴巴地说。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:597
translate Schinese chapter4_924d27d3:

    # e "What is it?"
    e "怎么了？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:599
translate Schinese chapter4_984171a4:

    # j "I'm glad you came here with me."
    j "我很高兴有你在这里陪我。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:601
translate Schinese chapter4_16d62b3b:

    # e "Me too. It's really beautiful here."
    e "我也是，这里真美。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:603
translate Schinese chapter4_ed57ff57:

    # "They stayed silent for a few minutes, Edgar enjoying the soft wet breeze."
    "他们沉默了几分钟，Edgar尽情享受着柔和而湿润的微风。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:605
translate Schinese chapter4_ecfbe96e:

    # j "... I wanted to tell you something."
    j "...我想告诉你一件事。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:607
translate Schinese chapter4_924d27d3_1:

    # e "What is it?"
    e "什么事？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:619
translate Schinese chapter4_c8545395:

    # j "... Ah, Nevermind."
    j "...呃，还是算了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:624
translate Schinese chapter4_fce58e06:

    # e "Hey, you can't just leave me hanging. Tell me!"
    e "嘿，别吊我胃口啊，快说！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:626
translate Schinese chapter4_0292be27:

    # j "(sigh) Well ok..."
    j "（叹气）好吧..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:631
translate Schinese chapter4_416e8ed2:

    # "Edgar said nothing and just stared at the ocean of lights."
    "Edgar一言不发，只是眺望着灯光的海洋。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:636
translate Schinese chapter4_dafe3dc0:

    # j "You've been the best friend I've ever had. Before you came my life was so dull and boring."
    j "你是我这辈子最好的朋友。在遇到你之前，我的人生是那么的单调和无聊。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:638
translate Schinese chapter4_c4304e85:

    # j "Just working to pay bills... going through the motions."
    j "只是打打工...做做样子。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:640
translate Schinese chapter4_b8480975:

    # j "But ever since you've stayed with me... it's been so exciting. I feel alive again."
    j "但自从和你一起生活...我感到无比兴奋，感到自己又活了过来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:642
translate Schinese chapter4_b69776d8:

    # "Edgar felt himself get red."
    "Edgar满脸通红。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:644
translate Schinese chapter4_0ee5fcf4:

    # e "H-hey... you've been my best friend too. I don't say it often enough but thanks for everything you've done for me."
    e "我-我不常说这种话，不过...你也是我最好的朋友，感谢你为我做的一切。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:646
translate Schinese chapter4_4d358803:

    # "James gave him a warm smile and placed his paw on Edgar's."
    "James给了Edgar一个温暖的微笑，并把爪子放在他的爪子上。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:650
translate Schinese chapter4_071a40d9:

    # "Edgar looked up at James. He was completely soaking, the rain dripping down his fur."
    "Edgar抬头望向James。他已经完全湿透了，雨水顺着他的毛发滴落下来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:652
translate Schinese chapter4_56eedc9a:

    # "Even in this darkness, he could see James' true self shining through."
    "即使身处黑暗，他仍能看到James真实的自我，熠熠生辉。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:654
translate Schinese chapter4_58828ae6:

    # "His eyes were deep, and Edgar felt a deep serenity looking into them."
    "Edgar注视着对方深邃的眼睛，感到内心无比平静。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:669
translate Schinese chapter4_81df4606:

    # "Edgar looked away into the shining city."
    "Edgar回过头，眺望起那座耀眼的城市。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:671
translate Schinese chapter4_d044ffb5:

    # "James looked onward as well, and took his paw off Edgar's."
    "James把爪子从Edgar那里挪开，也一并望向远方。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:675
translate Schinese chapter4_ef8deefb:

    # "James slowly came closer, and Edgar did the same."
    "James缓缓靠近Edgar，Edgar亦是如此。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:679
translate Schinese chapter4_ff70f371:

    # "Their lips came together. James was so much softer than Edgar could have possibly imagined."
    "他们的嘴唇凑在了一起，出乎Edgar的想象，James要温柔得多。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:681
translate Schinese chapter4_8ff99309:

    # "As they kissed, James parted Edgar's own lips with his tongue. They continued for a few seconds, until James shifted and turned towards Edgar."
    "James轻轻撬开Edgar的牙关，把舌尖探进他湿润的嘴中。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:683
translate Schinese chapter4_c2ee05a3:

    # "He held him closer, and continued his kiss with a deep ravenous hunger."
    "他更加用力地拥抱住他，怀着极度的渴望用力探索每一个角落。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:685
translate Schinese chapter4_27630f02:

    # "Edgar relaxed, letting James hold him up. Kissing him back, encouraging the strong wolf to take what was his."
    "Edgar逐渐瘫软，依偎在James的怀中，条件反射般回吻着他，鼓励着那只强壮的狼索取。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:687
translate Schinese chapter4_a24495f1:

    # "They continued in their wet kiss for a few minutes. After a while James pulled back."
    "他们的湿吻持续了数分钟。又过了一会，James才退回去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:691
translate Schinese chapter4_152bba6e:

    # j "Wow."
    j "哇。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:693
translate Schinese chapter4_8ac27acd:

    # e "That was... amazing."
    e "太...太棒了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:695
translate Schinese chapter4_7356d44f:

    # j "You're so beautiful. You don't know how long I've wanted to do that."
    j "你都不知道我忍了多久，你太迷人了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:697
translate Schinese chapter4_ad07e3de:

    # e "All this time?"
    e "这么久吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:699
translate Schinese chapter4_757cfdc7:

    # j "I'm sorry. I've never done this."
    j "这是我的第一次，见谅啦。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:701
translate Schinese chapter4_5bb80a41:

    # e "Me neither."
    e "也是我的第一次。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:703
translate Schinese chapter4_c3cb44c8:

    # "James grabbed Edgar's small paw in his and rubbed it."
    "James握住Edgar的小爪子，抚摸着。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:705
translate Schinese chapter4_cf889a72:

    # j "I really like you, you know?"
    j "我真是太喜欢你了，你知道吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:707
translate Schinese chapter4_dfcfc02c:

    # e "I like you too."
    e "我也喜欢你。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:709
translate Schinese chapter4_a79e1e34:

    # "Edgar couldn't help but smirk."
    "Edgar不禁傻笑了起来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:711
translate Schinese chapter4_c249949d:

    # "James smiled at leaned in for another kiss."
    "James微微一笑，又俯身落下一吻。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:713
translate Schinese chapter4_6684145d:

    # "Edgar met him again, feeling the wolf's warm tongue in his mouth."
    "Edgar也再度将狼的温暖的舌头吞进嘴里。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:715
translate Schinese chapter4_57b6b632:

    # "He felt the wolf embrace him fully, and Edgar put his smaller arms around his mane."
    "他感觉自己完全陷入了狼的臂膀，作为回应，Edgar用纤细的胳膊紧紧搂着狼的鬃毛。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:717
translate Schinese chapter4_85d946b2:

    # "They continued for a long time, then after a while stopped and then just hugged."
    "他们亲热了很长一段之间，然后停下来，仅仅拥抱着彼此。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:719
translate Schinese chapter4_6d65b1ce:

    # j "I was actually scared you know."
    j "其实我很害怕。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:721
translate Schinese chapter4_987e3d37:

    # e "Really?"
    e "真的吗？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:723
translate Schinese chapter4_436f1dde:

    # j "Yeah. I didn't know if you were..."
    j "嗯，我不知道你是不是..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:725
translate Schinese chapter4_2523758b:

    # e "Gay? You could have just asked you goof."
    e "同性恋？你大可直接问啊，傻瓜。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:727
translate Schinese chapter4_ed93faec:

    # j "That seemed a little too... weird."
    j "那也有点...太怪了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:729
translate Schinese chapter4_e8483595:

    # e "I guess I could have let you know too. I just don't usually talk about myself."
    e "我有打算告诉你的，只是我不常谈论自己。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:731
translate Schinese chapter4_c2d5f90e:

    # j "I know. I like how you're a shy guy."
    j "我知道，我喜欢你害羞的样子。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:733
translate Schinese chapter4_f70bc3ba:

    # e "I always felt kind of self conscious about it."
    e "我自己就从来没这么觉得。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:735
translate Schinese chapter4_706d4181:

    # j "Don't be. You're amazing the way you are."
    j "别这么说，你是一个很了不起的人。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:737
translate Schinese chapter4_503cf5eb:

    # "They stayed on the tower for a while longer, leaning on each other."
    "他们互相倚靠着，又在塔上呆了一会。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:742
translate Schinese chapter4_fe84cf58:

    # e "This city is so big..."
    e "这座城市好大啊..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:744
translate Schinese chapter4_6f1dcb47:

    # j "It feels like it goes on forever, right?"
    j "好像没有尽头一样，是吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:746
translate Schinese chapter4_ad072b87:

    # e "Yeah. My hometown was so much smaller. It was a coastal town."
    e "嗯，我的家乡就小得多，那是一座沿海小镇。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:748
translate Schinese chapter4_2946dc1c:

    # j "That sounds nice. What was it called?"
    j "听起来不错诶，叫什么名字？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:750
translate Schinese chapter4_f0de0a40:

    # e "Oceanica."
    e "大洋洲。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:752
translate Schinese chapter4_9b536934:

    # j "Haha, Sounds fitting."
    j "哈哈，还蛮贴切的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:754
translate Schinese chapter4_dd7d1d52:

    # e "Yeah.. maybe we can visit sometime."
    e "是啊...也许咱们可以抽空去看看。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:756
translate Schinese chapter4_4b9e6b70:

    # j "That would be cool."
    j "好主意。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:758
translate Schinese chapter4_bdfc6960:

    # "The fox and the wolf sat in silence for a while, nothing but the sounds of the rain and the whistling wind."
    "雨淅沥地下着，风呼啸地吹着，唯有狐狸和狼静静地坐在那里。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:760
translate Schinese chapter4_c51a0ebb:

    # j "I think we should get going."
    j "我想是时候回去了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:762
translate Schinese chapter4_f9b0707f:

    # e "Already? I'm really enjoying this."
    e "这么快？我还没享受够呢。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:764
translate Schinese chapter4_49727fbb:

    # j "Yeah but it's going to get dark soon. We still got a warm bed to go to."
    j "可天马上就要黑了，再说还有张暖和的床在等咱们。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:766
translate Schinese chapter4_5be3d705:

    # e "Alright... I hope we can come back here sometime."
    e "好吧...希望以后有机会再来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:768
translate Schinese chapter4_a0e50cd4:

    # j "Hah! And you didn't even wanna come at first!"
    j "哈！你一开始还不情愿呢！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:770
translate Schinese chapter4_8d28cc63:

    # e "Hey don't make me change my mind!"
    e "嘿，别逼我改变主意。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:772
translate Schinese chapter4_73946ca5:

    # j "Haha, alright. But I'm glad you liked it."
    j "哈哈，安啦，不过你喜欢就好。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:776
translate Schinese chapter4_b043be49:

    # "They climbed back down, and back through the vines."
    "他们爬下塔，穿过藤蔓。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:778
translate Schinese chapter4_15ec759b:

    # "They eventually made their way back toward the trail."
    "最终回到了小径上。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:780
translate Schinese chapter4_3a5ea14b:

    # "Everything was quiet except for the wind blowing and crickets in the distance."
    "四周鸦雀无声，除了风与远处的虫鸣。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:782
translate Schinese chapter4_20363410:

    # "There was a fine mist in the air, and they were both still soaking wet."
    "空气中弥漫着一层薄雾，他们二人依然浑身湿透。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:784
translate Schinese chapter4_b486a1c8:

    # "After climbing down the long trail, they made their way back into the city."
    "他们沿着长长的小径爬下山，返回了城市里。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:790
translate Schinese chapter4_d1c66487:

    # "The streets were mostly empty."
    "街道上几乎空无一人。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:792
translate Schinese chapter4_f86b29ac:

    # j "Oh... it looks like we can't get donuts tonight."
    j "啊...看来今晚买不到甜甜圈了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:794
translate Schinese chapter4_aa32cb28:

    # e "Ugh I had forgotten about that. Now I really want donuts."
    e "哎，为什么要让我想起来，现在我真的想吃甜甜圈了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:796
translate Schinese chapter4_cbd0c0d6:

    # j "We'll definitely get some next time, I promise."
    j "下次一定，我保证。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:798
translate Schinese chapter4_a6bde510:

    # e "Fine but you're paying for all my donuts."
    e "好吧，不过下次全由你买单。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:800
translate Schinese chapter4_4bac45b3:

    # j "Oh no.. I'll be bankrupt!"
    j "不...我要破产了！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:802
translate Schinese chapter4_6c47ee03:

    # e "That's what you get!"
    e "这是你自找的！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:804
translate Schinese chapter4_721338ab:

    # j "Haha... It'll be worth it."
    j "哈哈...倒也值了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:808
translate Schinese chapter4_994e8100:

    # "Edgar suddenly stopped."
    "Edgar突然停下脚步。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:812
translate Schinese chapter4_07227fe3:

    # "He heard the same noise as the night before. Something so subtle it could only be-"
    "他听到了和昨晚一样的动静，如此狡猾，这只能意味着-"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:814
translate Schinese chapter4_c90ffbf3:

    # "He looked behind him. All he saw was a few cars parked."
    "他回过头，只看到几辆车停在身后。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:818
translate Schinese chapter4_7c5d6758:

    # "His heart started beating faster."
    "他的心跳开始加速。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:820
translate Schinese chapter4_0d82aa70:

    # j "You ok?"
    j "怎么了？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:822
translate Schinese chapter4_083be7dd:

    # e "Y-yeah. Let's keep going."
    e "没-没什么。咱们接着走吧。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:824
translate Schinese chapter4_37e1acac:

    # "They continued walking, but they both remained quiet."
    "他们走在路上，却都保持着沉默。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:826
translate Schinese chapter4_a52db92b:

    # "Edgar quickened his pace as they went on, and James followed."
    "Edgar加快了脚步，James也跟在他后面。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:828
translate Schinese chapter4_20736040:

    # "There it was - a clean footstep. Whoever was following them was getting sloppy - or impatient."
    "有脚步声-非常明显的那种。跟踪他们的人要么变得草率-或是已经不耐烦了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:830
translate Schinese chapter4_fa550027:

    # e "On the count of three, run and follow me."
    e "我数三下，跟着我跑。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:832
translate Schinese chapter4_b1585b05:

    # j "Ok."
    j "好。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:834
translate Schinese chapter4_2b83a3d7:

    # "Edgar flicked the switch on his searing knife, turning it on."
    "Edgar轻轻拨开热熔刀上的开关。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:836
translate Schinese chapter4_c2106b81:

    # e "One."
    e "一。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:838
translate Schinese chapter4_1b12f5ad:

    # e "Two."
    e "二。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:840
translate Schinese chapter4_a7ddc911:

    # e "Three!"
    e "三！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:846
translate Schinese chapter4_80cc34fe:

    # "Edgar sprinted towards his target - an alleyway behind an apartment building."
    "Edgar狂奔向他的目标：公寓楼后的一条小巷。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:848
translate Schinese chapter4_fbef4803:

    # "James ran close behind."
    "James紧随其后。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:850
translate Schinese chapter4_b7dd8113:

    # "In the corner of his eye, Edgar detected a figure. He didn't get a good look as he entered the alleyway."
    "Edgar用眼角的余光扫到了一个人影，只是他正好拐进小巷，没有来得及看清楚。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:854
translate Schinese chapter4_c249bb6e:

    # "There was piles of garbage and trash cans. He dodged them and so did James."
    "James跟着Edgar避开巷子里成堆的垃圾与垃圾筒。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:856
translate Schinese chapter4_0fa6f81d:

    # "Edgar ran as fast as he could, and turned left into the corner. As they passed through, he heard a bullet zip past them."
    "Edgar拼了命的奔跑着，他向左拐进一个角落，同时听到一颗子弹从他们擦身而过。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:860
translate Schinese chapter4_ce5e20a1:

    # "He felt his adrenaline rushing. It was a silencer."
    "是消音器。他顿时感到肾上腺素激增。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:862
translate Schinese chapter4_0f54b416:

    # "He saw a door in the distance."
    "他看到远处有一扇门。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:864
translate Schinese chapter4_0a051e16:

    # "In one motion, Edgar took his hot knife and sliced the lock, and threw the door open, pushing James inside."
    "来不及多想，Edgar手起刀落把锁切开，将James推了进去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:866
translate Schinese chapter4_53d1c28a:

    # "Time almost came to a crawl."
    "时间都仿佛慢了下来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:868
translate Schinese chapter4_0be92a52:

    # "As he turned his head, another bullet whizzed by him, hitting the open door."
    "他刚想回头，另一颗子弹从他身边呼啸而过，击中了敞开的门。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:870
translate Schinese chapter4_efea4ffe:

    # "He flinched, the noise ricocheting like waves."
    "声音像波浪一样回荡在空中，他向后一缩。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:874
translate Schinese chapter4_4f87099a:

    # "He opened his eyes, and saw the dark figure up ahead, gun drawn, taking another step."
    "他睁开眼，看到前面那个黑影拔出枪，又向前迈了一步。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:876
translate Schinese chapter4_3cf5a6d5:

    # "As the figure pulled the trigger, James yanked him inside, the bullet striking the door again."
    "当那个人影扣动扳机时，James把他拉了进去，子弹再次击中了门。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:878
translate Schinese chapter4_adea2f0b:

    # "James led him through the dingy hallway, and up the stairs."
    "James带他穿过昏暗的走廊，爬上楼梯。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:882
translate Schinese chapter4_cb493030:

    # "They climbed as quickly as possible up three flights. Then they went into another hallway. The featureless doors blurred together."
    "他们以最快的速度爬到三层，接着进入另一条走廊。毫无特点的门混杂在一起，模糊不清。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:884
translate Schinese chapter4_477cb3cb:

    # j "Damn.. where do we go now?"
    j "可恶...咱们该怎么走？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:886
translate Schinese chapter4_a93e5a31:

    # e "I-I don't-"
    e "我-我不-"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:888
translate Schinese chapter4_31aa94fb:

    # j "Come on, Edgar. Breathe."
    j "冷静下来，Edgar，深呼吸。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:890
translate Schinese chapter4_e0454da8:

    # "Edgar stopped for a moment and took a breath."
    "Edgar停了下来，深吸一口气。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:892
translate Schinese chapter4_36cc0ce7:

    # e "The roof access.. that way."
    e "屋顶的入口...那边。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:894
translate Schinese chapter4_a8ecc688:

    # "They went over to the door and Edgar sliced the doorknob haphazardly."
    "他们来到门旁，Edgar胡乱切开了门把手。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:896
translate Schinese chapter4_c7c4e605:

    # "He could hear running footsteps behind them."
    "他能听到身后奔跑的脚步声。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:898
translate Schinese chapter4_e7862ab2:

    # "Edgar threw open the roof access door, and ran up the stairs into the roof."
    "Edgar猛地推开通往屋顶的门，沿楼梯跑了上去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:902
translate Schinese chapter4_38bf68c3:

    # "It was now or never - he had to make a split second decision."
    "时不我待，他必须立即作出决定。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:904
translate Schinese chapter4_d027c89d:

    # e "We have to jump to that building."
    e "咱们得跳到那栋楼上去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:906
translate Schinese chapter4_3327a0de:

    # j "A-alright."
    j "好-好的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:908
translate Schinese chapter4_55d71bc9:

    # "Edgar ran toward the edge of the building, and jumped the 6-foot gap. As he flew across, he felt his heart stop at the feeling of having a hundred feet of nothing under him."
    "Edgar跑向大楼边缘，一跃而起，跳过一道六英尺宽的缺口。望着下方空无一物的一百英尺，他的心脏几近骤停。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:910
translate Schinese chapter4_341a668a:

    # "He landed, and James landed next to him."
    "James降落在他身旁。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:912
translate Schinese chapter4_6e342745:

    # "Edgar turned into some A/C units, getting himself out of sight."
    "Edgar身形一转，隐藏在了空调机组中。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:914
translate Schinese chapter4_b6669829:

    # "He crouched and ran toward the fire escape, and climbed down with James closely behind."
    "他半蹲着跑向防火梯，二人先后爬了下去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:918
translate Schinese chapter4_9d938836:

    # "They went down, Edgar not daring to look up."
    "Edgar始终不敢抬头。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:920
translate Schinese chapter4_1ea577f2:

    # "Finally they got to ground level."
    "终于，他们抵达了地面。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:922
translate Schinese chapter4_07f9ca05:

    # e "This way."
    e "这边。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:924
translate Schinese chapter4_6e5b5e01:

    # "Edgar ran as fast as he possibly could away from the building, staying in the dark."
    "Edgar尽可能快地离开大楼，飞奔进夜色之中。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:926
translate Schinese chapter4_13933522:

    # "He went through alleyways, side streets."
    "他穿过一条又一条小巷。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:928
translate Schinese chapter4_ea29bbcb:

    # "So far, no sign of the assailant."
    "到目前为止，没有袭击者的踪迹。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:930
translate Schinese chapter4_95afd76f:

    # "After a while they slowed down. Both breathing in and out quickly."
    "又过了一会，他们放慢了速度，都上气不接下气。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:932
translate Schinese chapter4_806537da:

    # j "Did we lose him?"
    j "甩掉他了么？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:934
translate Schinese chapter4_73f272c2:

    # e "*Pant* I think so..."
    e "*喘气声* 也许吧..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:938
translate Schinese chapter4_81500ee6:

    # "They walked slowly in the semi-darkness. Both were quiet the whole time."
    "他们在明暗交加中慢慢地走着，谁也没有说话。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:940
translate Schinese chapter4_b7edeaf2:

    # "Edgar listened intently, but he heard nothing suspicious."
    "Edgar聚精会神地聆听着，不过并没有听到任何可疑之处。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:942
translate Schinese chapter4_012617a7:

    # "They walked in the general direction of James' apartment, until they finally made it back."
    "他们朝着James公寓的大致方向走去，直至终于到了家。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:952
translate Schinese chapter4_17e33f68:

    # j "Are you ok?"
    j "没事吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:954
translate Schinese chapter4_f2afd174:

    # e "Yeah... I'm fine."
    e "嗯...我不要紧。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:956
translate Schinese chapter4_aa0e85b0:

    # j "We gotta call the police. I can't believe we just got shot at!"
    j "得打电话报警才是，真不敢相信咱们差点就中枪了！"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:958
translate Schinese chapter4_ab163286:

    # e "No... they won't help us against this. Also they'd put two and two together, and find out who I am. My life would be over."
    e "不...警察不会帮咱们的。而且要是被他们把两件事联系起来，发现我是谁，我这一生就完了。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:960
translate Schinese chapter4_be15b06c:

    # "James furrowed his brow."
    "James眉头紧锁。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:962
translate Schinese chapter4_0a0e6b4c:

    # j "There's gotta be something we can do."
    j "一定还有其他办法。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:964
translate Schinese chapter4_ba8311d6:

    # e "I... shouldn't have brought you into this. I'm so sorry."
    e "我...不该把你卷进来的，对不起。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:966
translate Schinese chapter4_fcc28c5b:

    # j "It's alright.. You didn't mean for this to escalate so much."
    j "没什么...你也不是故意让事态升级的。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:968
translate Schinese chapter4_c6740ae2:

    # e "I just wanted to make it right... but maybe I can't."
    e "我只是想弥补...但恐怕我连这也做不到。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:970
translate Schinese chapter4_1ec42ece:

    # j "We'll find a way. I know it."
    j "振作起来。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:972
translate Schinese chapter4_d10c7972:

    # e "I could try contacting Mary again. Maybe she knows more information on who's behind this."
    e "我可以再联系Mary，也许她有幕后黑手的信息。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:974
translate Schinese chapter4_75864113:

    # j "Yeah that would be a good idea. Can't hurt, right?"
    j "嗯，试试也无妨，没错吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:976
translate Schinese chapter4_b0d319ec:

    # e "Alright... I'll see if I can do that tomorrow."
    e "好...我明天试试看。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:978
translate Schinese chapter4_d208aa8d:

    # "They sat in silence for a few moments."
    "他们默默地坐了一会。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:980
translate Schinese chapter4_b5ff0955:

    # j "It's been a long night. Let's go lay down, OK?"
    j "真是漫长的一夜，咱们休息吧？"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:982
translate Schinese chapter4_4ac09465:

    # e "... OK."
    e "...好。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:988
translate Schinese chapter4_4fadfb3d:

    # "They went into the bedroom and got onto the bed, turning off all the lights."
    "他们走进卧室，上了床，关掉了全部的灯。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:990
translate Schinese chapter4_765237bf:

    # "James snuggled next to Edgar, putting his arm around him."
    "James依偎在Edgar身边，用胳膊搂着他。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:992
translate Schinese chapter4_5faf58b5:

    # "Edgar felt the heat radiating from James. His torso rising and falling."
    "Edgar感受着James散发出的热量和起伏的躯干。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:994
translate Schinese chapter4_bfb69e2b:

    # "He felt so scared, but being in James' arms... it put him at ease."
    "他固然害怕，可James的怀抱...又令他感到安心。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:996
translate Schinese chapter4_6621b2b4:

    # j "Let's try to get some sleep..."
    j "试着睡一觉..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:998
translate Schinese chapter4_6361c8c3_1:

    # e "Yeah..."
    e "嗯..."

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1000
translate Schinese chapter4_3f1b1485:

    # "He felt strangely protected, like with James' big arm around him nothing could hurt him."
    "他产生了一种莫名的安全感，就好像James粗壮有力的手臂可以抵御一切伤痛。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1002
translate Schinese chapter4_309bc466:

    # "Edgar tried to close his eyes, but he saw him."
    "Edgar闭上眼睛，然而他的身影却挥之不去。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1004
translate Schinese chapter4_51d6b0ec:

    # "The man following them -"
    "那个跟踪他们的男人-"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1006
translate Schinese chapter4_71fc8452:

    # "He let out an exhasperated sigh."
    "他大声叹了口气。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1008
translate Schinese chapter4_83487bce:

    # "He tried to clear his mind."
    "他努力清空思绪。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1010
translate Schinese chapter4_e343b1cf:

    # "He breathed in and out, focusing on James' breathing next to him."
    "他吸气、呼气，把注意力集中在旁边James的呼吸上。"

# game/scripts/chapter4.rpy:1012
translate Schinese chapter4_ef4cab54:

    # "Eventually Edgar's body sank and he slept."
    "最终，Edgar身体一松，睡了过去。"

